Oak Industries said it signeda definitive agreement to buy the stock of Rexnord Inc'sRailway Maintenance Equipment Co unit, for an undisclosed sum.    The company said Railway Maintenance had 1986 revenues of16 mln dlrs.    Oak said the acquisition is part of its two-tier strategyof buying releated and unrelated businesses.    Oak had a tax loss carryforward of 125 mln dlrs at the endof 1986. Reuter&#3;